      {
        "id": "6cqQm9vf5R7rfFXq",
        "content": "SAM - Biz licenses",
        "description": "Regardless of municipality, most will ask for:\n\n- Legal business name\n- Doing‐Business‐As (DBA) name if applicable\n- Business physical address (within the municipality)\n- Mailing address (if different)\n- Owner(s) name(s) and contact info\n- Business type / nature of business (NAICS code in some cases)\n- Estimated gross receipts for the license year (or actual for renewals)\n- Number of employees (in some jurisdictions)\n- Registration/license numbers for special trades (e.g., contractors)\n- Proof of state registration if applicable (LLC, corporation, DBA)\n- Payment of application fee/license fee\n- Signature and date",
        "priority": "p2",
        "projectId": "6cwpf8hc6mJmFQM7",
        "sectionId": "6fC8vxvrjMW43VH7",
        "labels": [],
        "due": null,
